adjectives.description: insufficient (comparative more insufficient, superlative most insufficient)

entries.meaning: Not sufficient; of a type or kind that does not suffice, that does not satisfy requirements or needs.
examples: It is a necessary condition but an insufficient one.

entries.meaning: Not sufficient; lacking competent power or ability; unqualified, unequal, unfit.
